Widget<ChartWidget.Config>
public class ChartWidget
extends AbstractWidget<ChartWidget.Config>

Show the results of a query associated with an object. The class can be understood as a wrapper that maps the SPARQL data model (plus user config options) to the generic FChart class, which then renders the chart.
